{
  "doc_id": "24641",
  "text": "Work in estimating ARIMA parameters includes Amini et al. [CITATION_1] , and Boroojeni et al. [CITATION_2] . Amini et al. presented an approach to forecasting electrical vehicle charging using a decoupled ARIMA approach. The parameters of the ARIMA model are tuned to improve performance [CITATION_3] . Boroojeni et al. presented a two-tier demand forecasting approach to forecasting energy use and production on the smart grid. The two-tiers are a maximum likelihood estimator for longer durations and an ARIMA model for short term forecasting [CITATION_4] . They have also used a multi-seasonal ARIMA model to forecast the PJM interconnection [CITATION_5] .",
